Login as sysadmin (Password, same as root);
commands:
listdev - shows list of servers/devices connection settings on lightwave
editdev (edits lightwave port settings):
  editdev --name=server xx - (server = device name, xx = port number) - names port on lightwave
  editdev --type=1 xx - (xx = port number) - changes port setting to DCE
  dev xx - shows a ports current settings
less - shows previous console display


Edit a terminals settings:

Ctrl+numeric "-" - brings you to terminal settings
Esc - exits, select Y/N to save